The paper discusses the implementation of a search system for mathematical formulae in Wikipedia, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Digital Libraries (cs.DL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
